    {
      "id": "0Kx4RUnEfPne6gIgi44g-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 953.8394839529478,
      "y": -539.8321544794853,
      "width": 298.3597717285156,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0s",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1241675902,
      "version": 291,
      "versionNonce": 1686859298,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781654526126,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Both paths upload to MinIO input/ first:\n  Folder Watcher → detect file → upload to MinIO → notify Project Service\n  Front-end      → presigned URL upload → notify Project Service\nThen: Project Service runs FR6 check → creates job → triggers DAG",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Both paths upload to MinIO input/ first:\n  Folder Watcher → detect file → upload to MinIO → notify Project Service\n  Front-end      → presigned URL upload → notify Project Service\nThen: Project Service runs FR6 check → creates job → triggers DAG",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LpUUiuwh-P8QsCHlVP3kC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1485.3985220703216,
      "y": -729.1904575613625,
      "width": 725.5595703125,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0t",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 298530558,
      "version": 376,
      "versionNonce": 775717250,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781658236755,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "MinIO Buckets (lifecycle managed by storage):\ninput/       TTL 1h   — raw upload; Project Service copies → processing/ at job creation\nprocessing/  TTL 7d   — staged input + intermediates: segments.json, verify clips\noutput/      forever  — SRT, _summary.md/json, _corrected.srt, clean.wav",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MinIO Buckets (lifecycle managed by storage):\ninput/       TTL 1h   — raw upload; Project Service copies → processing/ at job creation\nprocessing/  TTL 7d   — staged input + intermediates: segments.json, verify clips\noutput/      forever  — SRT, _summary.md/json, _corrected.srt, clean.wav",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MObN9DL9_LCyMZfN4LB60",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1688.628091563676,
      "y": -497.25048967852695,
      "width": 439.8597992620517,
      "height": 214.86818331262486,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0u",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1378842046,
      "version": 821,
      "versionNonce": 134327371,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781875744798,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Project Service — on upload trigger:\n1. verify file exists in MinIO input/\n   (guard: upload may succeed but notify fail → let TTL clean up)\n2. FR6 security check: filename anomaly + size validation\n3. copy input/{job} → processing/{job}  ← 7d TTL; eliminates retry race\n4. if ok → create job in RDB → trigger DAG-Service\n5. if fail → reject, clean up processing/, do not trigger pipeline\n\nProject Service — correction write path (FR4):\n6. PATCH /jobs/{id}/correction received\n   → if unverified → auto-set verification_status = in_progress\n   → rebuild corrected SRT from segments array\n   → write MinIO output/{job}_corrected.srt\n   → update jobs.corrected_srt_path in RDB",
      "fontSize": 12.278181903578561,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Project Service — on upload trigger:\n1. verify file exists in MinIO input/\n   (guard: upload may succeed but notify fail → let TTL clean up)\n2. FR6 security check: filename anomaly + size validation\n3. copy input/{job} → processing/{job}  ← 7d TTL; eliminates retry race\n4. if ok → create job in RDB → trigger DAG-Service\n5. if fail → reject, clean up processing/, do not trigger pipeline\n\nProject Service — correction write path (FR4):\n6. PATCH /jobs/{id}/correction received\n   → if unverified → auto-set verification_status = in_progress\n   → rebuild corrected SRT from segments array\n   → write MinIO output/{job}_corrected.srt\n   → update jobs.corrected_srt_path in RDB",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "pw_note_bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 2554.17845736807,
      "y": -87.14012152200526,
      "width": 692.6758759039128,
      "height": 281.748931574472,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f59e0b",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 90,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0v",
      "boundElements": [],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "seed": 111111,
      "version": 237,
      "versionNonce": 320257468,
      "updated": 1781874414548,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "pw_note_text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2569.985106089977,
      "y": -77.37801513257006,
      "width": 631.0393676757812,
      "height": 260,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#92400e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0w",
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "seed": 111112,
      "version": 123,
      "versionNonce": 1939310140,
      "updated": 1781874410143,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Progress worker:\n1. ack MQ immediately on receive\n   (retry owned by DAG-Service, not MQ redelivery)\n2. download from processing/{job}  ← staged by Project Service at job creation\n3. run pipeline stages sequentially from resume_from_stage\n   (no fork/join — all stages in series, Phase 1)\n4. on each stage: update-status(stage, result) → DAG-Service via HTTP\n5. on complete: upload (overwrite) → output/\n   - {job}.srt, _summary.md/json, _segments.json\n   - clean.wav  ← kept forever for segment playback (on-demand clip source)\n   ▎ overwrite is safe: outputs are idempotent across retries\n6. on stage failure: update-status(failed) → DAG-Service\n   DAG-Service decides: retry (re-enqueue) or final failure",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Progress worker:\n1. ack MQ immediately on receive\n   (retry owned by DAG-Service, not MQ redelivery)\n2. download from processing/{job}  ← staged by Project Service at job creation\n3. run pipeline stages sequentially from resume_from_stage\n   (no fork/join — all stages in series, Phase 1)\n4. on each stage: update-status(stage, result) → DAG-Service via HTTP\n5. on complete: upload (overwrite) → output/\n   - {job}.srt, _summary.md/json, _segments.json\n   - clean.wav  ← kept forever for segment playback (on-demand clip source)\n   ▎ overwrite is safe: outputs are idempotent across retries\n6. on stage failure: update-status(failed) → DAG-Service\n   DAG-Service decides: retry (re-enqueue) or final failure",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rdb_note_bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 646.1101505913591,
      "y": 241.7584844162078,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 600,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#8b5cf6",
      "backgroundColor": "#f5f3ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 90,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0x",
      "boundElements": [],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "seed": 111113,
      "version": 199,
      "versionNonce": 26080300,
      "updated": 1781707962414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rdb_note_text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 661.1101505913591,
      "y": 253.7584844162078,
      "width": 430,
      "height": 580,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#4c1d95",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0y",
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "seed": 111114,
      "version": 216,
      "versionNonce": 1654034092,
      "updated": 1781707962414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "RDB — PostgreSQL  (Phase 1: single entity; split later)\n\n── jobs ─────────────────────────────────────────\n  id                  TEXT    PK\n  filename            TEXT    NOT NULL\n  submitted_by        TEXT    DEFAULT 'anonymous'\n  dag_flow_id         TEXT    FK → dag_flows.id\n  status              TEXT    NOT NULL\n    submitted | queued | processing | completed | failed\n  current_stage       TEXT\n  submitted_at        REAL\n  started_at          REAL\n  completed_at        REAL\n  retry_count         INT     DEFAULT 0\n  error_msg           TEXT\n  output_srt_path     TEXT\n  corrected_srt_path  TEXT\n  verification_status TEXT    DEFAULT 'unverified'\n    unverified | in_progress | verified\n  verified_at         REAL\n  verified_by         TEXT    ← reserved multi-user\n\n── dag_flows ────────────────────────────────────\n  id          TEXT   PK   e.g. \"course-v1\"\n  stage_plan  JSONB  NOT NULL  [{stage, config}]\n  is_default  BOOL   DEFAULT false\n  deprecated  BOOL   DEFAULT false\n  created_at  REAL\n  ▎ Phase 1: seed data only\n  ▎ Phase 2: API-manageable\n\n── events  (stage-level audit) ──────────────────\n  id             SERIAL  PK\n  job_id         TEXT    FK → jobs.id  NOT NULL\n  stage          TEXT    NOT NULL\n  status         TEXT    started | success | failed\n  retry_attempt  INT     DEFAULT 0\n  error_msg      TEXT\n  payload        TEXT    — full event JSON\n  ts             REAL    NOT NULL  (Unix epoch seconds)",
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "RDB — PostgreSQL  (Phase 1: single entity; split later)\n\n── jobs ─────────────────────────────────────────\n  id                  TEXT    PK\n  filename            TEXT    NOT NULL\n  submitted_by        TEXT    DEFAULT 'anonymous'\n  dag_flow_id         TEXT    FK → dag_flows.id\n  status              TEXT    NOT NULL\n    submitted | queued | processing | completed | failed\n  current_stage       TEXT\n  submitted_at        REAL\n  started_at          REAL\n  completed_at        REAL\n  retry_count         INT     DEFAULT 0\n  error_msg           TEXT\n  output_srt_path     TEXT\n  corrected_srt_path  TEXT\n  verification_status TEXT    DEFAULT 'unverified'\n    unverified | in_progress | verified\n  verified_at         REAL\n  verified_by         TEXT    ← reserved multi-user\n\n── dag_flows ────────────────────────────────────\n  id          TEXT   PK   e.g. \"course-v1\"\n  stage_plan  JSONB  NOT NULL  [{stage, config}]\n  is_default  BOOL   DEFAULT false\n  deprecated  BOOL   DEFAULT false\n  created_at  REAL\n  ▎ Phase 1: seed data only\n  ▎ Phase 2: API-manageable\n\n── events  (stage-level audit) ──────────────────\n  id             SERIAL  PK\n  job_id         TEXT    FK → jobs.id  NOT NULL\n  stage          TEXT    NOT NULL\n  status         TEXT    started | success | failed\n  retry_attempt  INT     DEFAULT 0\n  error_msg      TEXT\n  payload        TEXT    — full event JSON\n  ts             REAL    NOT NULL  (Unix epoch seconds)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
