      "updated": 1781734290289,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "verification_status flow:\n  unverified  → (job created)\n  in_progress → (first PATCH /correction, auto-set)\n  verified    → POST .../finalize\n  ▎ finalize also valid from unverified (no edits needed)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "verification_status flow:\n  unverified  → (job created)\n  in_progress → (first PATCH /correction, auto-set)\n  verified    → POST .../finalize\n  ▎ finalize also valid from unverified (no edits needed)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
