    {
      "id": "stage_dag_text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1584.8673009797787,
      "y": 692.1282757195472,
      "width": 475.9434509277344,
      "height": 157.5,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#7c2d12",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1i",
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "seed": 444004,
      "version": 15,
      "versionNonce": 1298226712,
      "updated": 1781706601937,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Stage plan (built from pipeline_config):\n  Always: preprocess → transcribe → summarize → [detect_chapters]\n  Optional (injected sequentially, in this order):\n    [verify_segments]  — after transcribe\n    [diarize]          — after verify_segments (or transcribe)\n                         ▎ speaker labels inserted before correct_srt;\n                           helps LLM resolve speaker-specific homophones\n    [correct_srt]      — after diarize (or verify_segments / transcribe)\n\n  All stages run sequentially (no fork/join in Phase 1)\n\n  resume_from_stage: skips all stages before failed node,\n                     re-runs failed stage + all downstream\n  ▎ stage outputs in MinIO processing/ are overwritten on retry (idempotent)\n  ▎ upstream outputs are preserved — no re-run of already-passed stages",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Stage plan (built from pipeline_config):\n  Always: preprocess → transcribe → summarize → [detect_chapters]\n  Optional (injected sequentially, in this order):\n    [verify_segments]  — after transcribe\n    [diarize]          — after verify_segments (or transcribe)\n                         ▎ speaker labels inserted before correct_srt;\n                           helps LLM resolve speaker-specific homophones\n    [correct_srt]      — after diarize (or verify_segments / transcribe)\n\n  All stages run sequentially (no fork/join in Phase 1)\n\n  resume_from_stage: skips all stages before failed node,\n                     re-runs failed stage + all downstream\n  ▎ stage outputs in MinIO processing/ are overwritten on retry (idempotent)\n  ▎ upstream outputs are preserved — no re-run of already-passed stages",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
