      "version": 15,
      "versionNonce": 991387268,
      "updated": 1781874365433,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Preset DAG Flows  (dag_flows seed data, Phase 1)\n\ncourse-v1\n  preprocess → transcribe → verify_segments\n             → correct_srt → summarize → detect_chapters\n\nmeeting-v1\n  preprocess → transcribe → diarize → summarize\n\ngeneral-v1  [is_default = true]\n  preprocess → transcribe → summarize\n\nSelection logic (Project Service, at job creation):\n  POST /jobs { dag_flow: \"course-v1\" }  → use specified flow\n  POST /jobs { }                         → use dag_flows.is_default row\n  ▎ No filename pattern matching — caller decides or falls back to default",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Preset DAG Flows  (dag_flows seed data, Phase 1)\n\ncourse-v1\n  preprocess → transcribe → verify_segments\n             → correct_srt → summarize → detect_chapters\n\nmeeting-v1\n  preprocess → transcribe → diarize → summarize\n\ngeneral-v1  [is_default = true]\n  preprocess → transcribe → summarize\n\nSelection logic (Project Service, at job creation):\n  POST /jobs { dag_flow: \"course-v1\" }  → use specified flow\n  POST /jobs { }                         → use dag_flows.is_default row\n  ▎ No filename pattern matching — caller decides or falls back to default",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
